753
00:46:17.694 --> 00:46:20.405
Ho? The man's an utter fucking liability.

754
00:46:20.489 --> 00:46:22.574
- Absolutely not.
- Ho comes back.

755
00:46:22.658 --> 00:46:25.452
He's the only one
who can manage my Deliveroo account.

756
00:46:30.832 --> 00:46:33.919
Fine. If he… Right. okay. Okay.

757
00:46:34.002 --> 00:46:38.298
So then. who do you propose
that we hang this on?

758
00:46:38.382 --> 00:46:42.719
Well. we pin it on the fucking chump
who deserves to go.

759
00:46:44.179 --> 00:46:45.889
- You.
- Me?

760
00:46:47.266 --> 00:46:49.977
No. No. No way. No.

761
00:46:50.060 --> 00:46:52.688
No. no. no. no. I'm not going anywhere.

762
00:46:53.272 --> 00:46:55.732
But you still paid a call girl.

763
00:46:55.816 --> 00:46:58.360
who. incidentally. you were also boffing.

764
00:47:00.612 --> 00:47:04.241
If you're not out of your office
within the hour.

765
00:47:04.324 --> 00:47:09.955
I'm gonna send this to every grubby
little hack I know from my drinking days.

766
00:47:10.038 --> 00:47:12.624
That's going to do untold damage
toward the Service and you know that.

767
00:47:12.708 --> 00:47:14.751
Like I give a fuck.

768
00:47:17.504 --> 00:47:19.256
Look what the Service has done to me.

769
00:47:19.840 --> 00:47:21.675
Yeah. and leave the door open
on your way out.

770
00:47:21.758 --> 00:47:23.927
I like a through draft.

771
00:47:30.017 --> 00:47:31.560
I'm sure we'll meet again.

772
00:47:32.394 --> 00:47:33.562
I doubt that.

773
00:47:34.438 --> 00:47:36.607
I don't use prostitutes.

774
00:47:36.690 --> 00:47:38.150
She wasn't a prostitute.

775
00:47:38.233 --> 00:47:39.443
She wasn't. that was…

776
00:47:39.526 --> 00:47:40.903
She wasn't… Oh. fuck.

777
00:47:40.986 --> 00:47:42.946
I don't know
where everybody gets this from.

778
00:47:43.655 --> 00:47:44.823
She… That was…

779
00:47:47.284 --> 00:47:48.660
She was an escort.

780
00:47:56.752 --> 00:47:59.004
Roddy Ho is on his way back to you.

781
00:47:59.713 --> 00:48:02.799
I am not taking Cartwright.

782
00:48:02.883 --> 00:48:04.218
Yeah. it's fine.

783
00:48:04.968 --> 00:48:07.054
I'm a little short on numbers anyway.

784
00:48:07.137 --> 00:48:08.138
You wanna keep him?

785
00:48:09.806 --> 00:48:10.807
You never know.

786
00:48:11.850 --> 00:48:14.645
Might need a new liver.

787
00:48:15.270 --> 00:48:19.775
Anyway. it was me that worked out
Whelan was the target--

788
00:48:19.858 --> 00:48:22.528
Don't tell me you want
to come back to the Park.

789
00:48:22.611 --> 00:48:23.987
Fuck off.

790
00:48:24.071 --> 00:48:29.159
Well. nice as it is to chat.
I'm in the middle of moving offices. So…

791
00:48:29.243 --> 00:48:30.953
Well. I hope that now you're First Desk

792
00:48:31.036 --> 00:48:32.913
you won't forget the little people.

793
00:48:33.413 --> 00:48:37.209
Door's always open for a coffee
and a catch up.

794
00:48:37.292 --> 00:48:39.127
Do I detect a note of sarcasm?

795
00:48:39.628 --> 00:48:41.004
Absolutely.

796
00:48:41.088 --> 00:48:45.592
I never wanna hear from you
or anyone else at the Park again.

797
00:48:46.093 --> 00:48:49.012
An arrangement that suits
both of us. Jackson.

798
00:49:00.732 --> 00:49:02.234
Would you just fuck off?

799
00:49:02.818 --> 00:49:04.319
Oh. it's nice to see you too.

800
00:49:06.363 --> 00:49:08.740
His dad stole a file…

801
00:49:09.408 --> 00:49:10.951
with the Slow Horses' names in it.

802
00:49:11.618 --> 00:49:15.581
Now he's dead
and my joes are being hunted.

803
00:49:17.165 --> 00:49:19.585
Slough House is completely missing.

804
00:49:20.169 --> 00:49:21.879
We don't exist anymore.

805
00:49:23.964 --> 00:49:26.925
You got a leak Julian Assange
would be proud of.

806
00:49:29.553 --> 00:49:31.096
Our security…

807
00:49:32.723 --> 00:49:33.932
in these hands.

808
00:49:36.101 --> 00:49:37.978
- We're running out of time.
- What?

809
00:49:38.604 --> 00:49:39.897
It's a bloodbath.

810
00:49:43.483 --> 00:49:45.360
- If you're in trouble…
- How dare you?

811
00:49:45.444 --> 00:49:47.321
- I'm the sort of person…
- Fuck do you think you are?

812
00:49:47.404 --> 00:49:48.864
…who would fuck up someone's day.

813
00:49:48.947 --> 00:49:50.616
What are you doing here?

814
00:49:52.201 --> 00:49:53.368
Business.

815
00:49:58.457 --> 00:49:59.833
No one is unaccountable. Diana.

816
00:50:01.418 --> 00:50:02.628
No one.

817
00:50:02.711 --> 00:50:04.713
We need to address the five Fs.

818
00:50:05.464 --> 00:50:08.008
Who the fuck. what the fuck.
where the fuck and why the fuck?

819
00:50:10.594 --> 00:50:11.595
That's four.

820
00:50:11.678 --> 00:50:13.931
Fuck off. That's five.

821
00:50:18.101 --> 00:50:19.937
Well. go on then. Fuck off.

